-- Fiat denies Chrysler deal already signed
-- 
-- Thu Apr 30, 2009 6:50am EDT
-- http://www.reuters.com/article/2009/04/30/us-autos-fiat-denial-sb-idUSTRE53T2PC20090430

 

 TURIN  (Reuters) - Fiat denied a newspaper report its long-awaited deal with U.S. car maker Chrysler LLC has already been signed. 

 Corriere della Sera newspaper reported on its website www.corriere.it earlier on Thursday that the deal had already been signed. "We are not confirming that," a Fiat spokesman told Reuters. Chrysler has until May 1 to reach agreement with Fiat on a survival deal. (Reporting by Gianni Montani, writing by Jo Winterbottom)